-- GFI’s Radcliffe Named as Dry-Bulk Head of Baltic Exchange Group
-- B y   M i c h e l l e   W i e s e   B o c k m a n n
-- 2013-01-04T17:05:29Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2013-01-04/gfi-s-radcliffe-named-as-dry-bulk-head-of-baltic-exchange-group.html
Ed Radcliffe, a freight-derivatives
broker at  GFI Group Inc. (GFIG) , was elected as this year’s chairman of
the Forward Freight Agreement Brokers Association for the dry-
bulk industry, the Baltic Exchange said.  The association is an independent group formed in 1997 that
represents freight-futures brokers, according to the London-
based exchange’s  website . The group also has a chairman
representing brokers for liquid cargoes.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Michelle Wiese Bockmann in London at 
